# Node / npm
node_modules/
*.tsbuildinfo
# Note: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored — the browser demo at /demo/
# imports compiled output via `../js/dist/index.js` over an external URL
# (raw.githack / GitHub Pages), so dist/ needs to be tracked. Re-run
# `npm run build` after source changes; commit the regenerated dist/.

